<p><strong>U5's signature AI partner.</strong> A perspective-taking coach that can role-play specific stakeholders in water-rights disputes — Tamil Nadu Cauvery delta farmer, Karnataka upstream farmer, Bengaluru urban consumer, Adivasi community member, downstream fisherman, environmental NGO, Cauvery Water Management Authority representative, and so on. Designed to make the <em>strongest</em> version of a stakeholder's argument so students rehearse responding to a well-formed opposite position rather than a caricature.</p>

